title.en: Tensei shitara Saiai no Kazoku ni Mouichido Deaemashita ~Afureru Ai wo Kono Hitosara ni Nosete~
Maid ni Tensei Shitara, Ukkari Ryuu Ou-sama no Ibukuro Tsukanja Imashita ~Moto Tips OL wa Saikyou Ryourijin?!~
Ochibure Saijo no Koufuku Heika ni Suterareta no de, Saiai no Hito wo Sukui ni ikimasu
Suterare Hanayome no Saikon - Koori no Henkyou Haku wa Saiai o Chikau
Kono Ai wa, Kokuou Heika no Gomeirei Janai - Ohitori-sama Kibou no Reijou desu ga, Funaka na Kishi ga Hanashitekuremasen!
Seiryaku Kekkon no Otto ni "Aisanakute Kekkou desu" to Sengen Shitara Dekiai ga Hajimarimashita
Niehime no Konin - Migawari Oujo wa Teikoku de Saiai to naru
Honmono no Seijo Janai to Bareta no ni, Outei Denka ni Semararete imasu
Hakoiri Koujou wa Shikou no Koi wo Onozomi desu! - Risou no Tonogata wo Sagasu Tabi ni Demasu. Tadashi, Utsukushisha Igai Mitomemasen!?
Tensei Jijou no Chiebukuro - "Jishou" Hitonami Kaishain deshita ga, Zense no Chishiki de Karei ni Otsukae Itashimasu!
Binbou Kishi ni Yomeiri Shita Hazu ga!? Yajin Reijou wa Koutaishihi ni Natte mo Ryuu wo Karitai
Konyaku Haki Shita Aite ga Mainichi Shazai ni Kimasu ga, Fukuen Nante Zettai ni Ariemasen!
Outaishi Denka wa Koukyuu ni Uranaishi wo Goshomou desu
Hametsu End Masshigura no Akuyaku Reijou ni Tensei shita no de, Oishii Gohan wo Tsukutte Kurashimasu
Ochikobore Reijou wa, Koushaku Kakka kara no Dekiai ni Kizukanai ~Konyakusha ni Shimeisareta no wa Saishoku Kenbi no Ane de wa Naku, Watashi deshita~
Watashi no Konyakusha-sama no Dokuzetsu ga Sugiru ~Minna ni Shio Taiou no Hazu ga Watashi wa Dekiai Sareteimasu~
